Subject: RE: [VB] Lug nut tightening/anti-seize grease


Be sure to apply about 72 foot pounds of torque to your lug nuts, as
specified in the books. - I don't use my torque wrench on them, but I've
learned how tight to make them with the 18 " bar, but not overtightened!

cal



